Comment: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,============正文===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,麥 回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等 我今天值日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢 笨蛋粟屋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.46,0:00:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我替你值日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 趕緊回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,路上順便吃個可麗餅什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,花火 要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要一起走呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,從高二之後 我們就很少一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最近 你都是和粟屋一起回去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是男朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,讓給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真不賴呢 粟屋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,粟屋很有女人緣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那兩人其實很般配不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你不和朋友一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 給我喝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,給我停下!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇死我了...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這誰呀
Comment: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,---標題---
